definition: to hand over/to deliver/to pay (money)/to turn over/to make friends/to intersect (lines)/variant of 跤[jiao1]

sentences.english: For the director of music. With stringed instruments.
sentences.chinese: 亞薩的詩歌，交與伶長，用絲絃的樂器。

sentences.english: "Neighbors separated only by a strip of water." This expression has been employed for a long time to describe the diplomatic communication and the friendship between China and Japan.
sentences.chinese: 一衣帶水一直被用來形容中日兩國之間的邦交與友誼。

sentences.english: He gave his people over also unto the sword; and was wroth with his inheritance.
sentences.chinese: 並將他的百姓交與刀劍，向他的產業發怒。

sentences.english: The Netherlands will continue to handle foreign and defence policy.
sentences.chinese: 荷蘭政府會繼續處理外交與國防政務。

sentences.english: Come to LiYuan home, the father will write letters to LiYuan hands.
sentences.chinese: 來到李淵家中，如意將父親寫的信件交與李淵手中。

sentences.english: The letter has been given to person concerned.
For the Father judges no man, but has committed all judgment to the Son.
sentences.chinese: 父不審判什麼人，乃將審判的事全交與子。

sentences.english: Payment by cash to be made only at the Centre.
sentences.chinese: 如以現款支付，請親臨本中心交與負責人。

sentences.english: For the Father judgeth no man, but hath committed all judgment unto the Son
sentences.chinese: 父不審判什麼人，乃將審判的事全交與子。

sentences.english: Natural crossing and boll setting of a nucleo-cytoplasmic sterile line of cotton Jin-A were studied.
sentences.chinese: 研究了晉A棉花質核不育系的天然異交與成鈴。

sentences.english: Travel service provider must report genuine ticket number that is valid for travel for an associated PNR.
sentences.chinese: 代理人應提交與旅行訂位記錄相關的真實有效的票號。

sentences.english: He put the rest of the men under the command of Abishai his brother, and they were deployed against the Ammonites.
sentences.chinese: 其餘的兵交與他兄弟亞比篩，對着亞捫人擺陣。

sentences.english: You are my south, north, intersecting and deviation, the line between.
sentences.chinese: 你的天南，我的地北，相交與背離，一線之隔。

sentences.english: Simply familiarise yourself with SL and submit examples of your work.
sentences.chinese: 只要瞭解自己，並提交與SL你的工作的例子。

sentences.english: And the rest of the people he delivered into the hand of Abishai his brother, that he might put them in array against the children of Ammon.
sentences.chinese: 其餘的兵交與他兄弟亞比篩，對着亞捫人擺陣。

sentences.english: For the choir director, with my stringed instruments.
sentences.chinese: 這歌交與歌詠長，用絲絃的樂器。
